    <description>
        <![CDATA[<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert"><button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
        <h3>Cookie Consent Neo - Atom for Gantry Framework</h3>
        <span aria-hidden="true" class="icon-user"></span>&nbsp;<em>Andreas Kar (andreas.kar@gmx.at)</em>
        <p><b>INFO</b>:&nbsp;Dieses Atom wurde für Gantry Helium installiert.<br />Wenn Sie das Atom für ein anderes Gantry Template installieren möchten, dann müssen die Dateien wie folgt platziert werden:</p>
		<ul><li><code>*.yaml</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/particles</code></li><li><code>*.twig</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/particles</code></li><li><code>*.js</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/js</code></li><li><code>*.css</code> =&gt; <code>/templates/[TEMPLATE]/custom/css</code></li></ul></div>]]>
    </description>
    <fileset>
        <files folder="particles" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/particles">
            <filename>cookie-consent-neo.html.twig</filename>
            <filename>cookie-consent-neo.yaml</filename>
        </files>
        <files folder="js" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/js">
            <filename>cookieconsent.3.0.6.min.js</filename>
            <filename>cookieconsent.3.0.6_mod.min.js</filename>
        </files>
        <files folder="css" target="templates/g5_helium/custom/css">
            <filename>cookieconsent.3.0.6.min.css</filename>
        </files>
    </fileset>
</extension>